description: Configuração de worktrees para Agents Payment Hub
alwaysApply: false

# Worktrees relativos ao diretório raiz do projeto
worktrees:
  - name: DOC-AGENT-0, DOC-AGENT-1, DOC-AGENT-2, DOC-AGENT-3, DOC-AGENT-4, DOC-AGENT-5, DOC-AGENT-6, DOC-AGENT-7, DOC-AGENT-8  
    path: .cursor/worktrees/payment-hub-api-docs
    branch: docs/payment-flows
  - name: DEV-IMPLEMENTATION-PLAN-AGENT-0
    path: .cursor/worktrees/payment-hub-api-implementation-commit-plan
    branch: planning/implementation-commit-plan
  - name: DEV-SETUP-AGENTE-0
    path: .cursor/worktrees/payment-hub-api-chore-project-setup
    branch: chore/project-setup
  - name: DEV-IMPLEMENTATION-MODULES, ARCH-REVIEW-AGENT-0
    path: .cursor/worktrees/payment-hub-api-feat-modules
    branch: feat/modules  

notes:
  - Use paths relativos para portabilidade entre máquinas
  - A branch main só deve ser atualizada via PR
  - Cada agente deve operar em seu worktree isolado
  - Commits e Git operations devem ocorrer dentro do worktree correspondente